    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and there isn't a single mark on it. It drives like a total dream and still has that fresh, new-car smell. If you\u2019ve been looking for perfection, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019d love for this to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have, so feel free to reach out!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
