      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The high-revving valvetrain remains quiet, with recent valve shim adjustments ensuring optimal clearance. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with TMS plates, and the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components for bulletproof reliability. The chassis remains taut, riding on factory-spec Sachs dampers and fresh bushings. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this slicktop retains its original VIN-matched panels and a factory-spec 3.64 limited-slip differential. A mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
