    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest possible standards by a meticulous owner. The exterior retains its deep, showroom-floor luster with zero swirl marks, chips, or dings, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, the bolsters are firm, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did on day one. Mechanically, it is flawless, accompanied by a comprehensive binder of every service record performed exclusively at the authorized dealership. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a perfect example of this model. It drives tight, quiet, and powerful, offering a 'new car' experience in every sense.",
      "price": 48500.0,
